channel.title: 317 Client Help?! (VIDEO) (BLA++!)
channel.description:
[size=15pt]I need some help. Ok, I moved onto 508 clients. Then I portfowarded (=D). Now I'd like to play 317's again but non of the clients work accept Miss Silabsofts. Even Moparscape doesn't work. Please. please help!
Here's a video.
[url=http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=219b42c&s=5]http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=219b42c&s=5[/url]
PLEASE, PLEASE HELP! IN THIS VIDEO I'M CLICKING ALL THE TIME THE MOUSE IS OVER LOGIN!
IT DOES THIS WITH EVERY IP, EXCEPT ON SILABSOFT.
[color=blue]IT'S EVER SINCE I PORTFOWARDED, I THINK?[/COLOR][/size]

item.title: 317 Client Help?! (VIDEO) (BLA++!)
item.dc:creator: @Dart_Zamaki Dart Zamaki
item.description:
@Dart_Zamaki wrote:

Either…

  • The server PORT is not right on the client
  • The server is not up at all
  • The firewall needs to be checked

I don’t know if there’s more but I think that would be the main issues that could
be the problem.
